text:
Trump-Trudeau awkward handshake: the funniest memes Donald Trump with Justin Trudeau has sparked a waves of handshake memes Credit: Reuters / Twitter / @SuppressThis Mark Molloy 14 February 2017 • 12:25pm 
The handshake was a huge talking point on social media, with one Twitter user joking: “Trudeau resisting Trump's weird handshake is the biggest display of dominance in the history of Canada.” Here are the funniest Trump-Trudeau handshake memes 1.
